metadata.name: The Ethereal Female #1
metadata.description:
I have worked with models for many years, photographing them as the human mannequin for many fashion industry creations. I’ve always been at odds with this portrayal and so my concept of ‘The Ethereal Ghost of the Female’ began to develop.  

An ethereal ghost of the female is how I began to perceive my human mannequins. Always seeing them but never actually showing them for who they really are.  

Ethereal - a true and pure beauty of the female is aesthetically enchanting while eliminating the aggression of the erotic.  

Ghost - a partially, fragmented, present entity that moves between the plains of the past, present, and future, naturally fading between them.

Female - the most powerful entity of the human race.

Photo© David Levine
